</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-02-02-0025-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-02-02-0025-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>GW deals with most of the points raised in this letter to Robinson in his letter of this date to Dinwiddie.</p>

